Title: Not Cancer
Plot: The team deals with an organ donor whose organs prove fatal, and the two surviving patients. Meanwhile, House hires a private detective to spy on Wilson, but hears a few things about himself that he'd rather not.
GuestStars: Michael Weston, Felicia Day, Tom Conlon, Elaine Kagan, Melissa Loprire, Christine Lucas, Denice Sealy, Tyler Patton, Eric Kaldor, Aimee Bell, Dennis Keiffer
